; Regression test for issue #729: Output of cleared doesn't align (BZ#729)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/729
;
; The cleared report's separator line had misaligned dashes: the second column
; used 16 dashes with a 4-space gap, but the data column is 18 chars wide with
; a 2-space gap. Fixed by changing the separator to match the column widths.

2000/01/01 * Payee One
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

2000/01/02 Payee Two
    Expenses:Books   $25.00
    Assets:Cash

2000/01/03 * Payee Three
    Expenses:Gas     $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test cleared
        $-175.00            $-150.00    00-Jan-03    Assets:Cash
         $175.00             $150.00                 Expenses
          $25.00                   0                   Books
         $100.00             $100.00    00-Jan-01      Food
          $50.00              $50.00    00-Jan-03      Gas
----------------  ------------------    ---------
               0                   0             
end test
